		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Special Drawing Rights</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>Special Drawing Rights</b> (<b>SDRs</b>) are potential claims on the freely usable currencies of <a href="/wiki/International_Monetary_Fund" title="International Monetary Fund">International Monetary Fund</a> members. SDRs have the <a href="/wiki/ISO_4217" title="ISO 4217">ISO 4217 currency code</a> XDR.</p>
